        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/359/361",
        "text": [
          "ه عن مسعدة بن زياد فقد رويته عن أبي؛ و محمّد بن الحسن- رضي اللّه عنهما- عن سعد بن عبد اللّه؛ و الحميريّ جميعا عن هارون بن مسلم، عن مسعدة ابن زياد."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "And whatever is narrated from Masadah ibn Ziyad, I have narrated it from my father and from Muhammad ibn Al-Hasan - may Allah (swt) be pleased with them - from Saʿd ibn Abdullah and Al-Himyari together, from Harun ibn Muslim, from Masadah ibn Ziyad."
          ]
        }
      }
